Hello I'm David, a strongbow drinker, International Hockey player and Front-end Developer/Designer based in London.

I currently work for Tui Travel as a Front-end Developer, closely with the UX team working on large scale projects.

A self confessed hockey nut, you'll see me running about at the weekends for Barnes HC.

My site is designed to be responsive. this means it adapts to the size of your screen, Built in Drupal 7 using the Omega HTML5 startup kit, Context and Delta modules for a few tweaks here and there.

The main font I have used is 'Lora' provided by Google Fonts, Georgia, and my logo is using Bebas.

See what i am upto on Github.
